{
  "texts": [
    "During training, the data is partitioned into batches, and the model's parameters are modified based on each cohort's average loss.",
    "The group size dictates the number of samples utilized during each update phase.",
    "A larger sample size can speed up the training rate but may require additional memory.",
    "CrossEntropyLoss was chosen as the experiment's loss function.",
    "During training, the model minimizes this loss function."
  ]
}